  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel is on a half board basis with meals taken in the hotels restaurant where you can enjoy typical Savoyard dishes.</p>
<p><span>A varied continental breakfast buffet with freshly baked pastries, regional products and fresh fruit is served each day. </span></p>
<p>Dinner consists of a three course menu with a choice, you can enjoy traditional cooking whilst admiring mountain views. Served between 7:30 - 9:30pm.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included.</p>
<p>There's also an a la restaurant open for lunch and dinner, which is not included with the hotel half board basis.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
