  <description><![CDATA[<p>Family run since 1967, the staff at the Hotel Les Flocons will be sure to make you feel welcome. With an excellent location at the foot of the pistes in 1550, getting on and off the mountain couldn't be easier, and when you return tasty evening meals and a wellness area awaits you.</p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>Sitting at the foot of the pistes in the village of <a data-udi="umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893}" title="Courchevel">Courchevel</a> 1550, this lovely hotel is in an enviable position. With the benefit of a village atmosphere, yet with easy access to the more lively Courchevel 1850, this hotel is perfect for having the best of both worlds. The hotel is located next to the piste and is a short walk away from the <span>Tovets chairlift which gives you excellent access to the world class ski area.</span></p>
<h2>Family owned</h2>
<p>The Hotel Les Flocons has been proudly run by the Obert family since 1967 and is known for its friendly staff and excellent food. The family have consistently improved the accommodation, with the bedrooms being furnished in a warm Savoyard style, boasting incredible views over the valley.</p>
<h2>Unwind and relax</h2>
<p>After a day on the slopes make the most of the wellness area in the hotel. Give your achy ski legs a break in the sauna or steam room or relax in the <span>hotels resident's bar  which has a fabulous south-facing terrace to soak up the winter sun.</span></p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with The Hotel Les Flocons making us the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
