  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Double Rooms</strong> sleep two people and are around 17m². These rooms overlook the mountains.</p>
<p><strong>South-Facing Double Rooms</strong> sleep two to three people and are around 20m². These rooms have a south facing balcony. Some rooms have an additional single bed for the third person.</p>
<p>Rooms for sole occupancy are available upon request, please call to book.</p>
<p>Twin rooms are available, just request when booking.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Mountain views</li>
<li>Satellite TV with English speaking channels</li>
<li>Alarm clock</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Separate WC</li>
<li>Bathroom with shower attachment</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Baby cots are available on request. Free for children under 2 years.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
